<lb n="0795c12" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead>佛說五王經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0795c13" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0795c14" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">失譯<note n="0795011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人名〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0795011"><lem wit="【大】">人名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>今附東晉錄</byline>
<lb n="0795c15" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT14p0795c1501"><note n="0795012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">昔＋（者）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0795012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">昔＋（者）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0795012"><lem wit="【大】">昔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">昔者</rdg></app>有五王，國界相近，共相往來，不相攻伐，
<lb n="0795c16" ed="T"/>唯作善友。</p><p id="pT14p0795c1605" place="inline">其最大者，字普安王，習菩薩行；
<lb n="0795c17" ed="T"/>餘四小王，常習邪行。大王<note n="0795013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（憐愍…之）六字＝愍之【宮】</note><app n="0795013" word-count="6"><lem wit="【大】">憐愍，意欲度之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">愍之</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0795c18" ed="T"/>呼來上殿，共相娛樂，乃至七日，終日竟夜，
<lb n="0795c19" ed="T"/>作倡伎樂。七日已滿，四<note n="0795014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝小王【三】【宮】</note><note n="0795014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王＝小王【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0795014"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">小王</rdg></app>共白<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" cf1="KI20n0863_p1227a08" wit="【CBETA】【麗】">大</lem><rdg wit="【大】">天</rdg></app>王言：「國
<lb n="0795c20" ed="T"/>事甚多，請還政治。」</p><p id="pT14p0795c2008" place="inline">大王語諸左右：「嚴駕車
<lb n="0795c21" ed="T"/>乘，群臣吏民都共送之。」</p><p id="pT14p0795c2110" place="inline">至其半道，大王憐
<lb n="0795c22" ed="T"/>愍，意欲度之，語<note n="0795015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（四王…言）十四字＝諸小王曰各說所樂悅樂之情一王答言【三】【宮】</note><note n="0795015a" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（四王…事）十一字＝諸小王曰各說所樂悅樂之情一王答言【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0795015a" word-count="14"><lem wit="【大】">四王言：「各說卿等所樂之
<lb n="0795c23" ed="T"/>事。」</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">諸小王曰各說所樂悅樂之情</rdg></app></p><p id="pT14p0795c2302" place="inline"><note n="0795015b" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一王言＝一王答言【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0795015b" word-count="14"><lem wit="【大】">一王言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">一王答言</rdg></app>：「我願欲得陽春三月樹木榮華，遊
<lb n="0795c24" ed="T"/>戲原野，是我<note n="0795016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所樂＝之樂【三】【宮】</note><note n="0795016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所樂＝之樂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0795016"><lem wit="【大】">所樂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">之樂</rdg></app>。」</p><p id="pT14p0795c2408" place="inline">一王復言：「<note n="0795017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我願欲得＝我所樂異願我【三】【宮】</note><note n="0795017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我願欲得＝我所樂異願我【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0795017"><lem wit="【大】">我願欲得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">我所樂異願我</rdg></app>
<lb n="0795c25" ed="T"/>常作國王，鞍馬服飾，樓閣殿堂，官屬人民
<lb n="0795c26" ed="T"/>圍遶左右，晃晃昱<anchor id="fxT14p0795c02"/>昱，<note n="0795018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">椎＝搥【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0795018" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>椎＝搥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0795018"><lem wit="【大】">椎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">搥</rdg></app>鍾鳴鼓，出入行
<lb n="0795c27" ed="T"/>來，路人傾目，是我之樂。」</p><p id="pT14p0795c2710" place="inline">一王復言：「我所樂
<lb n="0795c28" ed="T"/><note n="0795019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復異願＝異願復【三】【宮】</note><note n="0795019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復異願＝異願復【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0795019"><lem wit="【大】">復異，願</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">異願復</rdg></app>得好婦、好兒，端正無雙，共相娛樂，
<lb n="0795c29" ed="T"/>極情<note n="0795020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">快意＝快樂【宮】</note><app n="0795020"><lem wit="【大】">快意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">快樂</rdg></app>，是我之樂。」</p><p id="pT14p0795c2909" place="inline">一王復言：「我所樂復
<pb n="0796a" ed="T" id="T14.0523.0796a"/>
<lb n="0796a01" ed="T"/>異，願我父母常在，多有兄弟、妻子，羅列好
<lb n="0796a02" ed="T"/>衣美食，以恣其口，素<anchor id="fxT14p0796a01"/>琴<note n="0796001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">清衣＝青衣【三】＊【宮】</note><note n="0796001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">清衣＝青衣【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊【宮】</note><app n="0796001"><lem wit="【大】">清衣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">青衣</rdg></app>，共相娛樂，
<lb n="0796a03" ed="T"/><note n="0796002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是我之樂〕－【宮】</note><app n="0796002"><lem wit="【大】">是我之樂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。」</p><p id="pT14p0796a0305" place="inline">各自說其所樂竟，四王俱迴頭
<lb n="0796a04" ed="T"/>白其大王：「<note n="0796003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔王〕－【宮】</note><app n="0796003"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>所樂何事？」</p><p id="pT14p0796a0410" place="inline">大王答言：「我先說
<lb n="0796a05" ed="T"/>卿等<note n="0796004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所樂＝不樂【宮】</note><app n="0796004"><lem wit="【大】">所樂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">不樂</rdg></app>，然後說我之樂。卿一人言：『陽春
<lb n="0796a06" ed="T"/>三月樹木榮華，遊戲原野。』秋則<note n="0796005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">凋＝彫【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">凋＝彫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796005"><lem wit="【大】">凋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">彫</rdg></app>落，非
<lb n="0796a07" ed="T"/>是久樂。</p><p id="pT14p0796a0704" place="inline">「卿一人<note n="0796006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（復）＋言【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0796006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（復）＋言【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0796006"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">復言</rdg></app>：『願我常作國王，鞍馬服
<lb n="0796a08" ed="T"/>飾，樓閣殿堂，官屬人民圍遶左右，晃晃昱
<lb n="0796a09" ed="T"/>昱，椎<note n="0796007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鍾＝種【元】</note><app n="0796007"><lem wit="【大】">鍾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">種</rdg></app>鳴鼓，出入行來，路人傾目。』往古
<lb n="0796a10" ed="T"/>諸王，隱隱<note n="0796008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">闐闐＝軫軫【宋】【元】，賑賑【明】【宮】</note><note n="0796008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">闐闐＝軫軫【宋】【元】，＝賑賑【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796008"><lem wit="【大】">闐闐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">軫軫</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【宮】">賑賑</rdg></app>，快樂無極，福德轉盡，諸國
<lb n="0796a11" ed="T"/>相伐，忽然崩亡，非是久樂。</p><p id="pT14p0796a1111" place="inline">「卿一人<app type="＊" source="0796006"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">復言</rdg></app>：『願
<lb n="0796a12" ed="T"/>得好婦、好兒，端正無雙，共相娛樂，極情快意。』
<lb n="0796a13" ed="T"/>一朝疾病，憂苦無量，<note n="0796009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">非是＝此非【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">非是＝此非【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796009"><lem wit="【大】">非是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">此非</rdg></app>久樂。</p><p id="pT14p0796a1313" place="inline">「卿一人<app type="＊" source="0796006"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">復言</rdg></app>：
<lb n="0796a14" ed="T"/>『願我父母常在，多有兄弟、妻子，羅列好衣美
<lb n="0796a15" ed="T"/>食，以恣其口，素琴<app type="＊" source="0796001"><lem wit="【大】">清衣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">青衣</rdg></app>，共相娛樂。』一朝
<lb n="0796a16" ed="T"/>有事，為官<note n="0796010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所執＝所攝【宮】</note><app n="0796010"><lem wit="【大】">所執</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">所攝</rdg></app>，繫閉在獄，無有救護，此非
<lb n="0796a17" ed="T"/>久樂。」</p><p id="pT14p0796a1703" place="inline">四人俱問：「王樂<note n="0796011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">何事＝云何【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">何事＝云何【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796011"><lem wit="【大】">何事</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">云何</rdg></app>？」</p><p id="pT14p0796a1711" place="inline">王言：「我樂不生
<lb n="0796a18" ed="T"/>不死，不苦不<note n="0796012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惱＝樂【元】【明】</note><app n="0796012"><lem wit="【大】">惱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">樂</rdg></app>，不饑不渴，不寒不熱，存亡
<lb n="0796a19" ed="T"/>自在，此是我樂。」</p><p id="pT14p0796a1907" place="inline">四王俱言：「此樂何處？當有
<lb n="0796a20" ed="T"/>明師？」</p><p id="pT14p0796a2003" place="inline">大王答言：「吾師<note n="0796013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">號＋（曰）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">號＋（曰）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796013"><lem wit="【大】">號</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">號曰</rdg></app>為佛，近在<note n="0796014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祇桓＝祇洹【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">祇桓＝祇洹【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796014"><lem wit="【大】">祇桓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">祇洹</rdg></app>精
<lb n="0796a21" ed="T"/>舍。」</p><p id="pT14p0796a2102" place="inline">諸王歡喜，各詣佛所，<note n="0796015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔皆〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔皆〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796015"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>稽首作禮，退坐
<lb n="0796a22" ed="T"/>一面。大王胡跪，<note n="0796016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">叉手＝合掌【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">叉手＝合掌【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796016"><lem wit="【大】">叉手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">合掌</rdg></app>白佛言：「我等今得為
<lb n="0796a23" ed="T"/>人，<note n="0796017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鈍闇＝闇鈍【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鈍闇＝闇鈍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796017"><lem wit="【大】">鈍闇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">闇鈍</rdg></app>無<note n="0796018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智＝知【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">智＝知【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796018"><lem wit="【大】">智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">知</rdg></app>，但深著世樂，不知罪福，願
<lb n="0796a24" ed="T"/>佛為弟子等，說其苦諦。」</p><p id="pT14p0796a2410" place="inline">佛言：「卿等善聽！當
<lb n="0796a25" ed="T"/>為汝說。人生在世，常有無量眾苦切身，今
<lb n="0796a26" ed="T"/>粗為汝等略說八苦。何謂八苦？生苦、老苦、病
<lb n="0796a27" ed="T"/>苦、死苦、恩愛別苦、所求不得苦、怨憎會苦、
<lb n="0796a28" ed="T"/>憂悲惱苦，是為八苦也。</p><p id="pT14p0796a2810" place="inline">「何謂生苦？人死之
<lb n="0796a29" ed="T"/>時，不知精神趣向何道，<note n="0796019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">未得＝未知【宮】</note><app n="0796019"><lem wit="【大】">未得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">未知</rdg></app>生處，並受中
<pb n="0796b" ed="T" id="T14.0523.0796b"/>
<lb n="0796b01" ed="T"/>陰之形，至三七<note n="0796020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">日＋（中）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">日＋（中）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796020"><lem wit="【大】">日</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">日中</rdg></app>父母和合，便來受胎。一
<lb n="0796b02" ed="T"/>七日如薄酪；二七日如稠酪；三七日如凝酥；
<lb n="0796b03" ed="T"/>四七日如肉臠；五<note n="0796021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皰＝胞【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皰＝胞【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796021"><lem wit="【大】">皰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">胞</rdg></app>成就，巧風入腹，吹其
<lb n="0796b04" ed="T"/>身體；六情開張，在母腹中，生藏之下，熟藏
<lb n="0796b05" ed="T"/>之上。母噉一杯熱食，灌其身體，如入鑊湯；
<lb n="0796b06" ed="T"/>母飲一杯冷水，亦如寒&CB00457;切體；母飽之時，迫
<lb n="0796b07" ed="T"/><note n="0796022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迮＝逼【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迮＝逼【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796022"><lem wit="【大】">迮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">逼</rdg></app>身體，痛不可言；母饑之時，腹中了了，亦
<lb n="0796b08" ed="T"/>如倒懸，受苦無量。至其滿月，欲生<note n="0796023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之時〕－【宮】</note><app n="0796023"><lem wit="【大】">之時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>，頭
<lb n="0796b09" ed="T"/><note n="0796024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（下）＋向【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（下）＋向【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796024"><lem wit="【大】">向</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">下向</rdg></app>產門，<note n="0796025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔劇〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔劇〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796025"><lem wit="【大】">劇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>如兩石<note n="0796026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">挾＝夾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">挾＝夾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796026"><lem wit="【大】">挾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">夾</rdg></app>山；欲生之時，母危
<lb n="0796b10" ed="T"/>父怖，生墮草上，身體細軟，草觸其身，如履
<lb n="0796b11" ed="T"/>刀劍，忽然失聲大<note n="0796027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呼＝喚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呼＝喚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796027"><lem wit="【大】">呼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">喚</rdg></app>。此是苦不？」</p><p id="pT14p0796b1113" place="inline">諸人咸言：
<lb n="0796b12" ed="T"/>「<note n="0796028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＝實【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此＝實【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796028"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">實</rdg></app>是大苦。」</p><p id="pT14p0796b1205" place="inline">「何謂老苦？父母養育，至年長大，
<lb n="0796b13" ed="T"/>自用強健，擔輕負重，不自裁量，寒時極寒，
<lb n="0796b14" ed="T"/>熱時極熱，饑時極饑，飽時極飽，無有節度；漸
<lb n="0796b15" ed="T"/>至年老，頭白齒落，目視<note n="0796029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02884;&CB02884;＝茫茫【三】</note><note n="0796029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02884;&CB02884;＝茫茫【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0796029"><lem wit="【大】">&CB02884;&CB02884;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">茫茫</rdg></app>，耳聽不聰，盛
<lb n="0796b16" ed="T"/>去衰至，皮緩面皺，百節<note n="0796030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">痠＝痛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">痠＝痛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796030"><lem wit="【大】">痠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">痛</rdg></app>疼，行步苦極，坐
<lb n="0796b17" ed="T"/>起呻吟，憂悲心惱，識神轉滅，便旋即忘，命
<lb n="0796b18" ed="T"/>日促盡，言之流涕，坐起須人。此是苦不？」</p><p id="pT14p0796b1816" place="inline">大
<lb n="0796b19" ed="T"/>王答曰：「實是大苦。」</p><p id="pT14p0796b1908" place="inline">「何謂病苦？人有四大和
<lb n="0796b20" ed="T"/>合而成其身。何謂四大？地大、水大、火大、風大。
<lb n="0796b21" ed="T"/>一大不調，百一病生，四大不調，四百四病，
<lb n="0796b22" ed="T"/>同時<note n="0796031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">俱＝共【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">俱＝共【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796031"><lem wit="【大】">俱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">共</rdg></app>作。地大不調，舉身<note n="0796032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沈重＝皆痛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沈重＝皆痛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796032"><lem wit="【大】">沈重</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">皆痛</rdg></app>；水大不
<lb n="0796b23" ed="T"/>調，舉身<note n="0796033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00167;＝&CB00955;【宋】【元】，&CB00668;【明】，皆胖【宮】</note><note n="0796033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00167;＝&CB00955;【宋】【元】，＝&CB00668;【明】，＝皆胖【宮】</note><app n="0796033"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00167;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">&CB00955;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&CB00668;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">皆胖</rdg></app>腫；火大不調，舉身蒸熱；風大不
<lb n="0796b24" ed="T"/>調，舉身掘強，百節苦痛，猶被杖楚。四大進
<lb n="0796b25" ed="T"/>退，手足不任，氣力虛竭，坐起須人，口燥脣
<lb n="0796b26" ed="T"/>燋，筋斷鼻<note n="0796034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坼＝拆【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">坼＝拆【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796034"><lem wit="【大】">坼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">拆</rdg></app>，目不見色，耳不聞<note n="0796035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聲＝音【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聲＝音【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796035"><lem wit="【大】">聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">音</rdg></app>，不淨
<lb n="0796b27" ed="T"/>流出，身臥其上，心懷苦惱，言輒悲哀，六親
<lb n="0796b28" ed="T"/>在側，晝夜<note n="0796036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">看視初不＝看侍初無【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">看視初不＝看侍初無【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796036"><lem wit="【大】">看視初不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">看侍初無</rdg></app>休息，甘&CB00498;美食，入口
<lb n="0796b29" ed="T"/>皆苦。此是苦不？」</p><p id="pT14p0796b2907" place="inline"><note n="0796037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">答言＝王答曰【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">答言＝王答曰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796037"><lem wit="【大】">答言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">王答曰</rdg></app>：「實是大苦。」</p><p id="pT14p0796b2913" place="inline">「何謂死苦？
<pb n="0796c" ed="T" id="T14.0523.0796c"/>
<lb n="0796c01" ed="T"/>人死之時，四百四病，同時俱作，四大欲散，
<lb n="0796c02" ed="T"/><note n="0796038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魂魄＝魂神【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">魂魄＝魂神【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796038"><lem wit="【大】">魂魄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">魂神</rdg></app>不安。欲死之時，刀風解形，無處不痛，
<lb n="0796c03" ed="T"/>白汗流出，兩手摸空，室家內外，在其左右，
<lb n="0796c04" ed="T"/>憂悲涕<note n="0796039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">泣＝哭【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">泣＝哭【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796039"><lem wit="【大】">泣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">哭</rdg></app>，痛徹骨髓，不能自勝。死者去之，
<lb n="0796c05" ed="T"/>風去氣絕，火滅身冷，風先火次。魂靈去矣，
<lb n="0796c06" ed="T"/>身體<note n="0796040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">侹＝&CB13439;【宋】【宮】，挺【元】【明】</note><note n="0796040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">侹＝&CB13439;【宋】【宮】，＝挺【元】【明】</note><app n="0796040"><lem wit="【大】">侹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">&CB13439;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">挺</rdg></app>直，無所復知。旬日之間，肉壞血流，
<lb n="0796c07" ed="T"/>&CB00167;脹爛臭，甚不可<note n="0796041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道＝近【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道＝近【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796041"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">近</rdg></app>，棄之曠野，眾鳥噉食，
<lb n="0796c08" ed="T"/>肉盡骨乾，髑髏異處。此是苦不？」</p><p id="pT14p0796c0813" place="inline">答言：「實是大
<lb n="0796c09" ed="T"/>苦。」</p><p id="pT14p0796c0902" place="inline">「何謂恩愛別苦？室家內外，兄弟妻子，共
<lb n="0796c10" ed="T"/>相戀慕，一朝破亡，為人抄劫，各自分張，父
<lb n="0796c11" ed="T"/>東子西，母南女北，非唯一處，為人奴婢，各
<lb n="0796c12" ed="T"/>自悲呼，心內斷絕，窈窈冥冥，無有相見之
<lb n="0796c13" ed="T"/>期。此是苦不？」</p><p id="pT14p0796c1306" place="inline">答言：「實是大苦。」</p><p id="pT14p0796c1312" place="inline">「何謂所求不
<lb n="0796c14" ed="T"/>得苦？家有<note n="0796042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">財錢散用＝財物散盡【三】，財物散用【宮】</note><note n="0796042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">財錢散用＝財物散盡【宋】【元】【明】，＝財物散用【宮】</note><app n="0796042"><lem wit="【大】">財錢，散用</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">財物散盡</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">財物散用</rdg></app>追求，大官吏民，望得
<lb n="0796c15" ed="T"/>富貴，勤苦求之，求之不止，會遇得之，而作
<lb n="0796c16" ed="T"/>邊境令長。未經幾時，貪取民物，為人告言，
<lb n="0796c17" ed="T"/>一朝有事，檻車載去，欲殺之時，憂苦無量，
<lb n="0796c18" ed="T"/>不知死活何日。此是苦不？」</p><p id="pT14p0796c1811" place="inline">答曰：「實是大苦。」</p><p id="pT14p0796c1817" place="inline">「何
<lb n="0796c19" ed="T"/>謂怨憎會苦？世人薄俗，共居愛欲之中，<note n="0796043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">共諍＝爭【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">共諍＝爭【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796043"><lem wit="【大】">共
<lb n="0796c20" ed="T"/>諍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">爭</rdg></app>不急之事，更相殺害，遂成<note n="0796044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大怨＝大然【宋】</note><app n="0796044"><lem wit="【大】">大怨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">大然</rdg></app>，<note n="0796045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔各〕－【宮】</note><app n="0796045"><lem wit="【大】">各</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>自相
<lb n="0796c21" ed="T"/>避，隱藏無<note n="0796046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">地＝處【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">地＝處【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796046"><lem wit="【大】">地</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">處</rdg></app>，各磨刀錯箭挾弓持杖，恐<note n="0796047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">畏＝忽【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">畏＝忽【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796047"><lem wit="【大】">畏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">忽</rdg></app>
<lb n="0796c22" ed="T"/>相見，會遇<note n="0796048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迮＝狹【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迮＝狹【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796048"><lem wit="【大】">迮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">狹</rdg></app>道相逢，<note n="0796049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔各自〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔各自〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796049"><lem wit="【大】">各自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>張弓<note n="0796050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02088;＝注【三】，註【宮】</note><note n="0796050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02088;＝注【宋】【元】【明】，＝註【宮】</note><app n="0796050"><lem wit="【大】">&CB02088;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">注</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">註</rdg></app>箭，兩
<lb n="0796c23" ed="T"/>刀相向，不知勝負是誰，當爾之時，怖畏無量。
<lb n="0796c24" ed="T"/>此是苦不？」</p><p id="pT14p0796c2405" place="inline">答曰：「實是大苦。」</p><p id="pT14p0796c2411" place="inline">「何謂憂悲惱苦？人
<pb n="0797a" ed="T" id="T14.0523.0797a"/>
<lb n="0797a01" ed="T"/>生在世，長命者乃至百歲，短命者胞胎傷墮。
<lb n="0797a02" ed="T"/>長命之者，與<note n="0797001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其＝斯【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其＝斯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797001"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">斯</rdg></app>百歲，夜消其半，餘有五十
<lb n="0797a03" ed="T"/>年；在醉酒疾病，不知作人，<note n="0797002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797002"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">已</rdg></app>減五<note n="0797003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">歲＝年【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">歲＝年【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797003"><lem wit="【大】">歲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">年</rdg></app>；小
<lb n="0797a04" ed="T"/>時愚癡；<note n="0797004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">十五年＝五十年【宮】</note><app n="0797004"><lem wit="【大】">十五年</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">五十年</rdg></app><note n="0797005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">中＝過【三】</note><note n="0797005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">中＝過【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0797005"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">過</rdg></app>，未知禮儀；年<note n="0797006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">過＝中【三】</note><note n="0797006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">過＝中【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0797006"><lem wit="【大】">過</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">中</rdg></app><note n="0797007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">八十＝十五年中七十【宮】</note><app n="0797007"><lem wit="【大】">八
<lb n="0797a05" ed="T"/>十</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">十五年中七十</rdg></app>，老<note n="0797008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鈍＝耄【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鈍＝耄【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797008"><lem wit="【大】">鈍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">耄</rdg></app>無<note n="0797009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智＝知【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">智＝知【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797009"><lem wit="【大】">智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">知</rdg></app>，耳聾目冥，無有法則，復減
<lb n="0797a06" ed="T"/>二十年；已九十年，過餘<note n="0797010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔有〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔有〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797010"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>十歲之中，<note n="0797011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多諸憂愁＝多有諸愁憂【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多諸憂愁＝多有諸愁憂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797011"><lem wit="【大】">多諸
<lb n="0797a07" ed="T"/>憂愁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">多有諸愁憂</rdg></app>，天下欲亂時亦愁，天下旱時亦愁，天
<lb n="0797a08" ed="T"/>下大水亦愁，天下大霜亦愁，天下<note n="0797012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不熟＝大熱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不熟＝大熱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797012"><lem wit="【大】">不熟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">大熱</rdg></app>亦
<lb n="0797a09" ed="T"/>愁，室家內外多諸病痛亦愁，持家財物治生
<lb n="0797a10" ed="T"/>恐失亦愁，官家百調未輸亦愁，家人遭縣官
<lb n="0797a11" ed="T"/>事閉繫<note n="0797013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">牢獄＝在獄【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">牢獄＝在獄【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797013"><lem wit="【大】">牢獄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">在獄</rdg></app>未知出期亦愁，兄弟、妻子遠
<lb n="0797a12" ed="T"/>行未歸亦愁，居家窮寒無有衣食亦愁，比
<lb n="0797a13" ed="T"/>舍村落有事亦愁，社&CB01142;不辦亦愁，室家死亡
<lb n="0797a14" ed="T"/>無有財物、殯葬亦愁，至春時種作無有犁牛
<lb n="0797a15" ed="T"/>亦愁，如是種種憂<note n="0797014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悲＝愁【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悲＝愁【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797014"><lem wit="【大】">悲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">愁</rdg></app>，常無樂時，至其節日，
<lb n="0797a16" ed="T"/>共相集聚，應當<note n="0797015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">歡樂＝歡喜【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">歡樂＝歡喜【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797015"><lem wit="【大】">歡樂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">歡喜</rdg></app>，方共悲涕相向。此是
<lb n="0797a17" ed="T"/>苦不？」</p><p id="pT14p0797a1703" place="inline">答曰：「實是大苦。」</p>
<lb n="0797a18" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0797a1801">爾時，五王及諸群臣，會中數千萬人，聞<note n="0797016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛）＋說【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（佛）＋說【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797016"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">佛說</rdg></app>
<lb n="0797a19" ed="T"/>諸苦諦，心開意悟，即得須陀洹道，皆大歡
<lb n="0797a20" ed="T"/>喜，作禮而去。</p><p id="pT14p0797a2006" place="inline">四王俱白普安王言：「大王真
<lb n="0797a21" ed="T"/>是大權菩薩，化&CB00572;我等，令得道跡，大王之
<lb n="0797a22" ed="T"/>恩。我本觀諸宮殿，心情愛著，不能遠離，今
<lb n="0797a23" ed="T"/>&CB00418;宮殿，如視穢廁，無可<note n="0797017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">愛＝樂【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">愛＝樂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797017"><lem wit="【大】">愛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">樂</rdg></app>者。」即捨王位付
<lb n="0797a24" ed="T"/>弟，出家為道，修諸功德，日日<note n="0797018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＝無【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＝無【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797018"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">無</rdg></app>惓。</p></div1>
